    <entry>
      <title>hexo+github搭建博客</title>
      <link href="/2022/09/13/hexo-github-da-jian-bo-ke/"/>
      <url>/2022/09/13/hexo-github-da-jian-bo-ke/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="Hexo-GitHub博客搭建"><a href="#Hexo-GitHub博客搭建" class="headerlink" title="Hexo+GitHub博客搭建"></a>Hexo+GitHub博客搭建</h2><h3 id="一、环境准备"><a href="#一、环境准备" class="headerlink" title="一、环境准备"></a>一、环境准备</h3><p> <a href="https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1aV411p7Bc/?spm_id_from=333.788&vd_source=729cf6d80ca215d21822e34f9c4fb599">b站博客搭建详细讲解视频</a></p><ol><li>node.js   <a href="https://blog.csdn.net/qq_42006801/article/details/124830995"> Node.js安装与配置（详细步骤）_liyitongxue的博客-CSDN博客_nodejs配置</a></li><li>Git <a href="https://www.cnblogs.com/xueweisuoyong/p/11914045.html">Windows系统Git安装教程（详解Git安装过程） - 学为所用 - 博客园 (cnblogs.com)</a></li><li>编辑软件VScode</li><li>GitHub账号 <a href="https://github.com/">GitHub</a><ul><li>github访问加速：<a href="https://pan.quark.cn/s/4c170f5763d2">https://pan.quark.cn/s/4c170f5763d2</a> 提取码：sFNj</li><li>在github新建一个仓库</li></ul></li></ol><p><img src="https://xingqiu-tuchuang-1256524210.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/8770/image-20220910114147590.png" alt="image-20220910114147590"></p><p>仓库名设置为<strong>xxx.github.io</strong>, 后面必须是<strong>github.io</strong></p><p><img src="https://xingqiu-tuchuang-1256524210.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/8770/1.png" alt="1"></p><h3 id="二、Hexo安装部署"><a href="#二、Hexo安装部署" class="headerlink" title="二、Hexo安装部署"></a>二、Hexo安装部署</h3><ol><li>Hexo安装</li></ol><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash">npm install hexo -g<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><ol start="2"><li>初始化博客</li></ol><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash">hexo init [博客文件]<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><ol start="3"><li>安装依赖</li></ol><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash">npm install<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><ol start="4"><li>预览 （现在可以在本地看看博客模板）</li></ol><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash">hexo serve<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><p><strong>注意：</strong>终端位置需切换到blog目录下</p><img src="http://xingqiu-tuchuang-1256524210.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/8770/2.png" alt="2"  /><h3 id="三、主题优化"><a href="#三、主题优化" class="headerlink" title="三、主题优化"></a>三、主题优化</h3><h4 id="3-1关键页面生成"><a href="#3-1关键页面生成" class="headerlink" title="3.1关键页面生成"></a>3.1关键页面生成</h4><p>可以直接按着官方教程做<a href="https://github.com/blinkfox/hexo-theme-matery">https://github.com/blinkfox/hexo-theme-matery</a></p><ul><li>标签页</li></ul><blockquote><p>进到hexo根目录，打开git, 执行</p></blockquote><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash">hexo new page tags<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><blockquote><p>打开 source&#x2F;tags&#x2F;index.md 文件，修改如下：</p></blockquote><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash">---title: tagsdate: 2018-09-10 18:23:38type: &quot;tags&quot;layout: &quot;tags&quot;---<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><ul><li>分类页</li></ul><blockquote><p>进到hexo根目录，打开git</p></blockquote><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash">hexo new page categories<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><blockquote><p>打开 source&#x2F;categories&#x2F;index.md 文件，修改如下</p></blockquote><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash">---title: categoriesdate: 2018-09-30 17:25:30type: &quot;categories&quot;layout: &quot;categories&quot;---<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><ul><li>个人介绍页</li></ul><blockquote><p>进到hexo根目录，打开git</p></blockquote><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash">hexo new page &quot;about&quot;<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><blockquote><p> 打开&#x2F;source&#x2F;about&#x2F;index.md文件，修改如下</p></blockquote><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash">---title: aboutdate: 2018-09-30 17:25:30type: &quot;about&quot;layout: &quot;about&quot;---<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><ul><li>留言栏</li></ul><blockquote><p>进到hexo根目录，打开git</p></blockquote><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash">hexo new page &quot;contact&quot;<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><blockquote><p> 打开&#x2F;source&#x2F;contact&#x2F;index.md文件，修改如下</p></blockquote><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash">---title: contactdate: 2018-09-30 17:25:30type: &quot;contact&quot;layout: &quot;contact&quot;---<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><ul><li>友情链接</li></ul><blockquote><p>进到hexo根目录，打开git</p></blockquote><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash">hexo new page &quot;friends&quot;<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><blockquote><p> 打开&#x2F;source&#x2F;friends&#x2F;index.md文件，修改如下</p></blockquote><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash">---title: contactdate: 2018-09-30 17:25:30type: &quot;friends&quot;layout: &quot;friends&quot;---<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><h4 id="3-2新建文章"><a href="#3-2新建文章" class="headerlink" title="3.2新建文章"></a>3.2新建文章</h4><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash">hexo new post &quot;文章名&quot;<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre>]]></content>
      
      
      
